3. Expected Output


---

1️⃣ GET Request

URL:

http://localhost:8080/RestAPI/rest/students/list

Output:

ID : 101   Name : John Doe
ID : 102   Name : Jane Smith


---

2️⃣ POST Request (Add Student)

URL:

http://localhost:8080/RestAPI/rest/students/create?id=103&name=Alex

Output:

Student Added : Alex (ID : 103)


---

3️⃣ GET Again

ID : 101  Name : John Doe
ID : 102  Name : Jane Smith
ID : 103  Name : Alex


---

4️⃣ PUT Request (Update)

URL:

http://localhost:8080/RestAPI/rest/students/update?id=103&name=Alex Brown

Output:

Student 103 Updated to : Alex Brown


---

5️⃣ DELETE Request

URL:

http://localhost:8080/RestAPI/rest/students/delete/103

Output:

Student Removed : Alex Brown (ID : 103)


